{
  "stem": "6130.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They needed workers, and that's why we were shipped out of Auschwitz after three, three and a half weeks, sometime in August.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But meanwhile, we were dying from thirst.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were dying from hunger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We got a horrible-looking soup which wasn't soup, just gray-ish water looking like bark of a tree in it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it's-- it's strange, but we all had diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had no food, but we had diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were big latrines, and we were standing in line for the latrines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was a little pool left over from some rain, and we almost drank from it, but it looked yellow from urine, so we didn't.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then my niece and I, we had a very-- very serious conversation how to commit suicide, because it was impossible to live through that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm sure we wouldn't have another week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Hunger, thirst, heat-- scorching heat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were all full of blisters from the heat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And if you just moved the wrong way, the Aufseherinnen, which are the supervisors with the whip, ran and hit you wherever they could reach you with the whip.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And dogs all over-- barking dogs, threatening dogs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was hell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a barbed wire-- first we thought we can hang ourselves, but we had nothing to hang ourselves with.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We looked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't find any rope or anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were very serious about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we thought, maybe we can do something with the electric wire, but what can we do?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A wagon came by some days with water, but if you didn't happen to find a cup, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you didn't have water.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
